title: Hotel Montmartre -la Tour d'Auvergne
description:
Well located hotel, just a few steps away from rue des Martyrs, Montmartre, Gare du Nord, Opéra, and avenue Trudaine. This is a district where you can find authentic places, good restaurants, small cafés and bistros, nice shops and true Parisian atmosphere.

It is located near numerous concert venues such as La Cigale, Divan du Monde and Elysées .
